title: Bda Maka Ska (formerly Lake Calhoun)
posting_body: ['Available September 1st.', 'Large, well cared for Upper Duplex just 3 short blocks East of Bda Maka Ska (formerly Lake Calhoun) and 1 block West of Hennepin Ave.', 'Just 5 blocks South of Lake & Hennepin yet without the parking hassle and noise of Uptown.', 'Located on a very quiet street with mostly single family homes.', 'Just around the corner from Dunn Bros. Coffee.', 'There is a 1 Car Attached Garage plus off-street parking for 4 vehicles during those pesky snow emergencies.', 'In addition, Street Parking is abundant!', 'This unit is spacious, light and airy with mostly South Facing Windows.', '3 good size bedrooms and 2 baths (including a 3/4 with shower off the master bedroom.)', 'Natural Oak Flooring through-out.', 'Even a Fireplace in the Living Room!', 'Lots of natural woodwork with built in china cabinets in the Formal Dining Room and bookshelves in the Living Room.', 'The Kitchen has granite counter tops, newer stainless refrigerator, new dishwasher and a separate breakfast room with a full wall of cabinets.', 'Coin-op laundry in a spacious, clean, well lighted space.', 'Resident pays for cable, heat and electricity.', 'There is a private, lockable storage room for each unit.', "It's a nice, quiet building and neighborhood and I am looking for new residents who will appreciate that in their new living space.", 'All prospective residents must attend the showing.', "Please wear a mask for everyone's safety.", '(Thnx)', 'Available Septemnber 1st.', 'For a prompt response call or text Brian at', 'show contact info', '.']
